334
1366
00:31:44,820 --> 00:31:47,043
What do you mean scissors!

335
1370
00:31:47,090 --> 00:31:48,380
I'll get it free.

336
1374
00:31:48,386 --> 00:31:50,748
Sorry, but I don't have time.
I'll just cut it off.

337
1379
00:31:50,800 --> 00:31:52,600
Hold on! STOP!

338
1383
00:31:54,022 --> 00:31:57,722
See what happens if you cut my hair. I'll sue you.

339
1387
00:32:20,111 --> 00:32:21,973
