377
1547
00:36:34,080 --> 00:36:37,796
Mister, please go where this Miss is going.

378
1551
00:36:37,796 --> 00:36:39,542
Mister, I don't agree with him.

379
1555
00:36:39,542 --> 00:36:42,400
